  <brief_title>Intravenous Remifentanil Plus Morphine or Morphine Alone for Postthoracotomy Pain</brief_title>
  <official_title>COADMINISTRATION OF INTRAVENOUS REMIFENTANIL AND MORPHINE FOR POSTTHORACOTOMY PAIN; COMPARISON WITH IV MORPHINE ALONE</official_title>
  <sponsors>
